se,"type":"Activities::Comment","message":"Hi @intidc,\n\nI know we're looking forward to reading the write-up. As you get closer to publishing information would you mind letting us know? We've discussed some solutions for resolving this vulnerability but as it pretty much affects only gitlab.com and we've blocked it from being exploited for any sensitive services it's been allowed to stagnate a bit. We'll do our best to get a patch out before September, but if we fail we'd really appreciate a heads-up before it goes public.\n\nWhen a patch is released we'll let you know right away. Thanks again,","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2017-08-03T00:59:31.628Z","updated_at":"2017-08-03T00:59:31.628Z","actor":{"username":"briann","cleared":false,"url":"/briann","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"/assets/avatars/default-71a302d706457f3d3a31eb30fa3e73e6cf0b1d677b8fa218eaeaffd67ae97918.png"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":false},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"gitlab","actor_is_team_member":false,"actor_is_concealed_member":false},{"id":1887782,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::Comment","message":"Absolutely - I'll let you know. From what I found, this affects Slack, Yammer and Phabricator. Will ping you in September so you can proofread it.","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2017-08-03T09:27:36.688Z","updated_at":"2017-08-03T09:27:36.688Z","actor":{"username":"intidc","cleared":true,"url":"/intidc","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/002/322/cb30ac31b7653e73d6dd5a0f0e2cfeed113d2feb_original.jpg/fd4ecbe1e3e98c343c7717114485ace2f830f9253103d3cfa7502059868c516c"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":false},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"gitlab","actor_is_team_member":false,"actor_is_concealed_member":false},{"id":1984694,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::Comment","message":"Hi @briann,\n\nI'd like to publish the 